<p class="ql-align-center">黔北山岭之中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一处古鰼国遗世的村落</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">飞鱼图腾，岁月千年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200907/b92979cd24154eed9c877d517ce5eb51.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">四面浅山包裹</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">风过处，一曲清溪流淌而出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">稻香梯田、飞鸟绕谷</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这里便是鰼部族人世代安居的乐土</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200907/d14ce016f83b4663984805c17dc79cef.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
